Wins awarded for left to right adjacent symbol combinations of any size.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with new symbols coming from above. New symbols are of the same size as the initial spin result, before tumbles.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
Special reels are in play during FREE SPINS feature.
The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently. The possible values are:
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.
Only the highest win is paid per winning combination on the same pay way.
When winning on multiple pay ways, all wins are added to the total win.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

During the free spins round WILD symbols hit with a random multiplier of 2x, 3x or 5x. Every time a WILD is involved in a winning combination it's multiplier is accumulated in a tumble multiplier indicator. All WILD multipliers that hit during a tumble sequence multiply between each other. At the end of the tumble sequence the accumulated multiplier applies to the total win of that tumble sequence.
Hit 3 or more BONUS symbols during the feature to win 5 more free spins.

serializableData._text: Visi simboliai imokami i kairs  dein ant gretim rii pradedant nuo kairiosios puss.
Laimjimai apdovanojami i kairs  dein didjaniomis bet kokio dydio simboli kombinacijomis.

KRATYMO YPATYB reikia, kad po kiekvieno sukimo, laimingos kombinacijos yra imokamos ir visi laimingi simboliai dingsta. Lik simboliai krenta  ekrano dugn ir laisvos vietos yra pakeiiamos naujais simboliais i viraus. Nauji simboliai yra tokio pat dydio kaip pradinio sukimo rezultate, prie sukratym.
Kratymas tsis tol kol nebeliks laiming kombinacij kaip kratymo rezultatas.
Visi laimjimai pridedami prie aidjo balanso po vis kratini rezultato i suaisto pagrindinio sukimo.
Specialios rits dalyvauja aidime, NEMOKAM SUKIM metu.
aidjas turi galimyb pasirinkti statymo daugikl. Priklausomai nuo pasirinkto statymo, aidimas elgiasi skirtingai. Galimos verts yra:
Didelio kintamumo aidimai vidutinikai imoka maiau, taiau galimyb laimti dideles sumas i ma sukim skaiiaus kur kas didesn.
Tik didiausias laimjimas imokamas i laimtojo kombinacijos pergals eilje.
Kai laimima keliais bdais, visi laimjimai pridedami prie bendro laimjimo.
Visi laimjimai ireikti kaip tikri laimjimai monetomis.
Pasibaigus raundui nemokam sukim laimjimas suteikiamas aidjui.
Nemokam sukim bendras laimjimas istorijoje laiko viso ciklo laimjim.
Gedimai anuliuoja visus imokjimus ar aidimus.

Nemokam sukim raundo metu WILD simboliai isukami su 2x, 3x arba 5x daugikliu. Kiekvien kart, kai WILD simbolis isukamas ekrane, jo daugiklis kaupiamas grities daugiklio indikatoriuje. Visi WILD simbolio daugikliais, kurie isukami grities sekoje, daugina vienas kit. Grities sekos pabaigoje sukauptas daugiklis taikomas bendram grities sekos laimjimui.
Isukite 3 arba daugiau BONUS simbolius per funkcij, kad laimtumte dar 5 nemokamus sukimus.
Jei perkate NEMOKAM SUKIM funkcij, isukami 4, 5 arba 6 BONUS simboliai atsitiktinai dovanoja 12, 17 arba 22 nemokam sukim.
WILD simboliai atsiranda tik ant 2, 3, 4 ir 5 bgn.
